In the MATTER OF PUAH B., et al., etc. Autumn B., Appellant;
v.
Administration for Children's Services, Respondent, Hemerd B., Respondent. Court of Appeals of New York. Decided on August 29, 2019

Appeal dismissed without costs, by the Court sua sponte, upon the ground that the order appealed from does not finally *1319determine the proceeding within the meaning of the Constitution.
